INSTALL

Prerequisites: a standard C compiler
in src/ folder type make install
the d2D+.x executable will be copied
in the bin/ folder

## PLEASE CHECK THAT THE d2D INSTALLATION DIRECTORY IS DEFINED IN NEXT LINE!!!
## and add them to your terminal configuration file (.bashrc or .profile)

export CAMDBV3=/Users/carlo/Codes/d2D
export PATH=$PATH:$CAMDBV3/bin

d2D+.x -h will show an help screen
